description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! I love space games, and a part of me was hoping for this expansion to make a new space IP known as Starfield actually a fun game. The day passed and I realized that since the developer for this was Bethesda that was a fairy tale that could never come true. Thanks for watching!

title: Bethesda Is Dead...
